<HEAD>Elephants Kill One Man, Hippo Wounds Another</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NAIROBI, Kenya (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Rampaging elephants trampled a man to
death in southeastern Kenya, and a hippopotamus emerged from a
