<HEAD>Death Toll in Rockslide Climbs to 52</HEAD>
<DATELINE>FEZ, Morocco (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The death toll from a rockslide that
demolished a squatter's camp climbed to 52 on Sunday, and rescue
workers were searching for more victims beneath the debris,
officials said.
   At least six people were injured, one seriously, when a rock
wall overhanging the camp collapsed about Saturday after a week of
